<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Gradual Simples on O Repertório Litúrgico</title><link>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/tags/gradual-simples/</link><description>Recent content in Gradual Simples on O Repertório Litúrgico</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>pt-br</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/tags/gradual-simples/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Gradual Simples - Tempo Comum</title><link>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-tempo-comum/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-tempo-comum/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-tempo-comum/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Gradual Simples - Tempo Comum" /&gt;&lt;h1 id="gradual-simples"&gt;Gradual Simples
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Para o tempo comum, o gradual simples traz 8 opções de antífonas de Entrada, Ofertório e Comunhão, que em conjunto fazem uma &amp;ldquo;Missa&amp;rdquo;. Sendo repertórios possíveis para cantar durante todos os dias do tempo comum, sejam domingos ou não, resolvi deixar em uma publicação separada.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-i"&gt;Missa I
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Toda a terra vos adore com respeito e proclamo o louvor do vosso nome, ó Altíssimo&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Missal Romano Sl 65, 4)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/Mr6WYcYTquE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/C8wcQ-1h80U" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Cantando Antífonas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/SC3mmOtU_WU" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. Carlos Silva&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/4Fk1SNadPKo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Delphim Rezende Porto&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/S4sjLQRl5ZI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gilson Celerino&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://ocantonaliturgia.pt/obras/746/Toda-a-terra-Vos-adore-J-A-Nunes" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;João Andrade Nunes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/_vEwgtNtPg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/hCLY5dIOaC8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Virgilio Solli&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/sgzYY9yk804" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Gritai a Deus aclamações de alegria!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 46(47), 2b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/lrhT3WRVp0A?si=-IiCJE79IUJsS16m" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Agnaldo Armindo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/p7l-pyandfQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Todos eles se admiravam das palavras proferidas pelos lábios do Senhor!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Lc 4, 22)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/7iuD_MvBCr4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-ii"&gt;Missa II
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;em&gt;Para mim fostes sempre um socorro&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 62, 8a)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/22H2sovnJUk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;em&gt;Ficai atento ao clamor da minha prece, ó meu Rei e meu Senhor&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 5, 3)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/E50CR5zrvBo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/doYQua_xGcY?si=dzT9d3r6PgkkhEG2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Eder Peçanha&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/NgkVwzbB3c0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel - Missa Cantada&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/1V5aZ3ZMxDc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;em&gt;Que eu vos cante pelo bem que me fizestes!&lt;/em&gt; (Cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 12, 6c)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/FNe4fu_SXBk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/idHVSkU-i4E" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Cantando Antífonas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/C5CntomX59M?si=Bv8pHgjvfONjA0OM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. José Fernandes da Silva&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/E__HHFH-m_E" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Maike Siman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/4I32jrTW5yg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/53mS5vZnvxQ?si=bn-2Lz7RvpgUcIiK" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcelo Koychi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-iii"&gt;Missa III
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Senhor, voltai-vos para mim, tende piedade&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 118, 132a)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/krWYD4AMqHY" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/X46Is81lDSo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Quem me protege e me ampara é meu Deus&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 53, 6a)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/yeuBKm59ggg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/Bf1qgZrlKII" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. José Weber, SVD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/BuuKKoSUz-A" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;J. Francisco (Adapt. Mônica Siqueira)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/hfQf7Vhq_C4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/NP2rn-Sgxz8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Buscai em primeiro lugar o Reino de Deus e a sua justiça e todas essas coisas vos serão dadas por acréscimo. Aleluia&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Missal Romano Mt 6, 33)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/WmaHjKqdzaE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/WDrQGSSFEK8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/aDHPmDcGzwU" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Rosa de Jesus, OCDS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-iv"&gt;Missa IV
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Recebemos, ó Deus, a vossa misericórdia no meio do vosso templo.&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Missal Romano Sl 47, 10)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CRvnIdfHURb/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/MP5_05tyemk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Clayton Dias&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ykh8PH5QkIE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Emerson Firmino&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/5h0-g7vPReo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. José Weber, SVD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/6XNNc02KLNY" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/gH9JGWU-nRQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Mônica Siqueira&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/2-0b5cMn4vM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Paulo Neto&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/KRAXSf7d7f4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Virgilio Solli&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Não deixeis vosso servo sozinho, porque sois para mim Salvação!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 37, 22a.23b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CRvvtxJFBOE/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Adorai-o no esplendor da santidade&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 95, 9a)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CRzBJyzrbI1/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-v"&gt;Missa V
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;O Senhor inclinou para mim o seu ouvido!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 114(116 A), 2)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CSrcM2tp09h/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/pQ2mXoHqPnE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ks0IeJ1Ko4c" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Não deixeis que se me apague a luz dos olhos&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 12, 4b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CSrrZ-6Fsiq/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ZEW5QoWvzCc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/2gr-VVaiuwI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/6xsg9Rn94mI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pastoral da Música - Paróquia Santo Expedito&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Cantai ao nosso Deus, porque é suave&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 146(147A), 1b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CSr3XHeLjR8/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/BhNKUMWgkbk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-vi"&gt;Missa VI
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Concedei-nos, Senhor, a paz em nossos dias pois não há quem lute por nós, senão vós, Senhor Deus.&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas e Bíblia CNBB Sr 50, 25 e Ne 4, 20)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CUOB94RFfOe/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/QSemdbNSgN8?si=rjYIbN27lnsjz4xO" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/oHCv8VGeWoU?si=ME8DujHJ1PBJ6WNL" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Fazei o bem, Senhor, aos bons e aos que têm reto coração&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 124, 4)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CUP14xWr6kK/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/DJzpTNJa3nk?si=Beg0kJOVY4SZLBlK" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/bAcHYgvIUAo?si=D4RrB3irKe2RQLGI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Amparai-me e serei salvo, ó Senhor!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 118, 117)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CUP1-SGttaw/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/YrIbIYRxyic?si=riGmxEcPjvl3PfbJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/EA_OZ28wPEM?si=uhKjwTRKrwcEa5DZ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-vii"&gt;Missa VII
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Vós que habitais nos altos céus, tende piedade de nós&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 122, 1.3)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtube.com/shorts/8UR2fG9KIic?si=A7Tv1RpmR-eZKwNw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Adriano José e Lívia Canêdo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/djpa2dfM0YI?si=c3Mm-Uh5Azeom6xx" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Felizes os que temem o Senhor&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 127, 1)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtube.com/shorts/rDBpQWOcrO0?si=2gkKeAwpsyMvN9Lx" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Adriano José e Livia Canêdo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/0ctQhqIT9WE?si=nW_jP4KMd60ybyLm" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Vós nos destes os vossos mandamentos para serem fielmente observados&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 118, 4)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtube.com/shorts/BeqCtsCOaPE?si=wl1X1G5mTWRtnOM0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Adriano José e Livia Canêdo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/W806QgGc_6A?si=OEG_rR8yPXx2oa8c" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/-PQx-xTD2Zs?si=13VEjrPjx8kk3Jas" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Cantando Antífonas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/aOFE221nphg?si=CP123zrUiAOhONpC" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcelo Koychi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/fKuxrovVqZ4?si=GL6YPkIKzRGxd5FM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Virgilio Solli&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/0D6aJ1RlTUs?si=Zcf6qKFoAGX_YriL" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="missa-viii"&gt;Missa VIII
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Bendito seja o nome do Senhor agora e por toda a eternidade&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 112, 2)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/BAgWhId3jNw?si=AfBdKXMOXJaiQ8G9" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Do nascer do sol até o seu ocaso, louvado seja o nome do Senhor&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 112, 3)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/TfHPXP4zPso?si=h2iOV-2FmXB-EfR9" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Provai e vede quão suave é o Senhor&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 33, 9)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ncVOu9HhBAM?si=j7QaCszOaUtQxXJ7" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Gradual Simples - Advento</title><link>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-advento/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-advento/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="gradual-simples"&gt;Gradual Simples
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="missa-i"&gt;Missa I
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;A vós, ó meu Deus, eu elevo a minha alma: libertai-me porque sois o meu refúgio, ó Senhor.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt; (Liturgia das Horas Sl 142, 8d.9b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/d_649Xk4MUg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/RMW25_S0Grw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/_72j0fQm96E?si=joKzDquM9tm80XIP" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Não será desiludido quem em vós espera.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt; (Missal Romano Sl 24, 3)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/RXwyk0JRz6c" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/l876_vSadgk?si=zYW-CuNR5ipEQwZr" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;O Senhor dará a sua bênção, e nossa terra, o seu fruto&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; (Missal Romano Sl 84, 13)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/o7YDve6UC2U" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/jkAeevxkT6U" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra 2ª Opção&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/WU0Zx6k-caY" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Clayton Dias&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/xKKALpt0hyM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Emerson Firmino&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/NxxWeqUG62I?si=uiSAXr8R0njR1zNT" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gilson Celerino e Fr. Wanderson L. F., O. Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/824ZQDN5nPo?si=MaX5M6ws2rx5hUGX" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gradual Simples em Vernáculo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ZWnl73t7mY4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Joel Postma, OFM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/JXqkMEAEX5M" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Mônica Siqueira&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ULcR0YjLdxU" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O. Carm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="missa-ii"&gt;Missa II
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Céus, deixai cair o orvalho, nuvens, chovei o justo; abra-se a terra, e brote o Salvador!&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt; (Missal Romano Is 45, 8)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/k-BS3HRulFQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/s-MDuEEO850" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Cantando Antífonas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/QZ2awMZD81I" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/iwT80AfOWXo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. Joaquim dos Santos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/JVTG5IIeem4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/0iGvEzKcvPY" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Ir. Miria T. Kolling&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/Tgm2j0rcMSk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;Ave, Maria, Cheia de graça, o Senhor é convosco. Bendita sois vós entre as mulheres, e bendito é o fruto do vosso ventre.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt; (Missal Romano Lc 1, 28.42)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/PCj_Q7-aTzA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/O6uRyGRTAiQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/tibmNx2pmiI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback II&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/5dRNeXvpMc4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;&lt;em&gt;Gregoriano&lt;/em&gt; adapt.: Gabriel Coelho Soares&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Favorecestes, ó Senhor, a vossa terra.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt; (Liturgia das Horas Sl 84, 2)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/jfq-eZfE0Xc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Gradual Simples - Páscoa</title><link>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-p%C3%A1scoa/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.orepertorioliturgico.com.br/p/gradual-simples-p%C3%A1scoa/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="gradual-simples"&gt;Gradual Simples
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="missa-i---tempus-paschale"&gt;Missa I - Tempus Paschale
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Eu sou o bom pastor e conduzo minhas ovelhas. E pelas minhas ovelhas eu dou a minha vida, Aleluia&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Lecionário Jo 10, 14.15)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CNcv12TJpl7/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Ansioso desde a aurora vos busco para ver vosso poder ó Senhor Deus. Aleluia&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 62, 2)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CNcy5QoJJ6e/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Na Galileia vereis Jesus, como Ele havia dito. Aleluia!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Lecionário Mc 16, 7)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CNc0n2_p8aS/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="missa-ii---tempus-paschale"&gt;Missa II - Tempus Paschale
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Entrada:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Cantai ao Senhor Deus um canto novo, louvor a ele dos confins de toda a terra!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Is 42, 10)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/-lGWuWe4-GM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/uhjp8HpNcO8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Cantando Antífonas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/VfXXPl91LVI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Pe. José Weber, SVD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/N8t3-tgs1eQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Marcela Buback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/spNiW136948" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Mons. Marco Frisina&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/lozFK1BiQX4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Valentino Miserachs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ZF5MHGzj7fc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Ofertório:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Gritai a Deus aclamações de alegria! Aleluia&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 46, 2b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/p7l-pyandfQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Angelo La Serra&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Antífona de Comunhão:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Cantai ao Senhor Deus e bendizei seu santo nome! Aleluia!&lt;/em&gt; (cf. Liturgia das Horas Sl 95, 2b)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/spNiW136948" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Mons. Marco Frisina&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://youtu.be/ZF5MHGzj7fc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Fr. Wanderson Luiz Freitas, O.Carm.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>